verbose_text: When available, laboratory values (e.g., CRP levels, erythrocyte sedimentation rate [ESR]) and measures of radiographic progression (e.g., Bath Ankylosing Spondylitis Radiology Index, modified Stoke Ankylosing Spondylitis Spine Score [mSASSS]), and spinal mobility (e.g., Schober test, occiput-to-wall distance) were also extracted.
